        <span><h2>Currently based in California</h2></span>
        <p>☹︎ WEBSITE CURRENTLY UNDER CONSTRUCTION ☺︎</p>
        <a class="logo-linked-in" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/romaincapelle/" target="_blank">
